From 4ab5361632cb56a643d574bbddfdee80a14016a6 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Dan on Selwyn <dan@awto.au>
Date: Wed, 20 May 2026 15:40:30 +1000
Subject: [PATCH 06/20] iso: add isochronous IN skeleton across gateware,
 firmware, and Python
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Gateware (awtoau/cynthion#13):
- ep_iso_in.py: new CSR peripheral wrapping USBIsochronousStreamInEndpoint
  with FIFO-backed DATA register and BYTES_IN_FRAME arming per USB frame
- top.py: wire ep_iso_in (ep1, 128-byte) into usb0 target PHY; requires
  bitstream rebuild before the hardware path is active

Firmware (awtoau/cynthion#13):
- moondancer.rs: track TransferType per endpoint in configure_endpoints
- moondancer.rs: add iso_in_write verb (0x10) stub — logs calls, returns OK;
  full CSR write path is TODO pending bitstream rebuild and PAC regen

Python (awtoau/facedancer vendor/facedancer submodule awto branch):
- proxy.py: route isochronous IN endpoints to _proxy_iso_in_transfer
- proxy.py: _proxy_iso_in_transfer uses libusb1 isochronous transfer
- proxy.py: LibUSB1Device.isoRead() synchronous isochronous read wrapper
- backends/moondancer.py: send_iso_in_frame() calls GCP verb 0x10

Infrastructure:
- vendor/facedancer: awtoau/facedancer fork as git submodule (awto branch)
- cynthion/python: editable install; moondancer.bin tracked in source tree
- .gitignore: un-ignore cynthion/python/assets/moondancer.bin

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
 .gitignore                                    |   3 +-
 .gitmodules                                   |   3 +
 cynthion/python/assets/moondancer.bin         | Bin 0 -> 55044 bytes
 .../src/gateware/facedancer/ep_iso_in.py      | 164 ++++++++++++++++++
 .../python/src/gateware/facedancer/top.py     |  14 +-
 firmware/moondancer/src/gcp/moondancer.rs     |  84 ++++++++-
 vendor/facedancer                             |   1 +
 7 files changed, 264 insertions(+), 5 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 .gitmodules
 create mode 100755 cynthion/python/assets/moondancer.bin
 create mode 100644 cynthion/python/src/gateware/facedancer/ep_iso_in.py
 create mode 160000 vendor/facedancer

diff --git a/.gitignore b/.gitignore
index 979b66e..099022a 100644
--- a/.gitignore
+++ b/.gitignore
@@ -39,7 +39,8 @@ Thumbs.db
 tags
 
 # files involved in generating a release
-cynthion/python/assets/moondancer.bin
+# awto: moondancer.bin is our patched build, tracked in source
+!cynthion/python/assets/moondancer.bin
 cynthion/python/assets/*.bit
 cynthion/python/assets/**/*.bit
 cynthion/python/VERSION
diff --git a/.gitmodules b/.gitmodules
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..cc84220
--- /dev/null
+++ b/.gitmodules
@@ -0,0 +1,3 @@
+[submodule "vendor/facedancer"]
+	path = vendor/facedancer
+	url = https://github.com/awtoau/facedancer
diff --git a/cynthion/python/assets/moondancer.bin b/cynthion/python/assets/moondancer.bin
new file mode 100755
